channel.title: Urbandy - Jelly [Synth Beats?]
channel.description:
My new track "Jelly" was made entirely using Auxy. :auxy: From my latest album BEATTAPE—a collection of 13 lush, downtempo electronic beats.
https://soundcloud.com/urbandy/jelly
![urbandy-beattape|500x500](upload://lyxvT3OWu8W5pUe41pUUW5sX3R9.jpg)
Auxy has totally improved my workflow. I can get my ideas out so much faster now, it's insane. :sunglasses:
-andy
